# This is the directory the running api container reads mapping
# documents from at boot. SENTRY_INBOUND_MAPPINGS_DIR (default
# /db/mappings, matching the docker-compose ./db:/db volume mount)
# resolves here.
#
# Operators writing their first mapping doc: start with
# `example-template.yaml.template` in this directory. Copy to
# `<source_system>.yaml`, edit, drop in an inbound_source_systems_allowlist
# row, restart api.
#
# See db/migrations/037_wms_tokens_inbound_columns.sql for the
# inbound_source_systems_allowlist DDL.
